				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "When players have encountered Orin and had a companion abducted, Orin would have given the players an ultimatum.\r\n\r\nOrin will send messages to the players at key points.\r\n1) When players first fight a Steel Watch at the end of that combat.\r\n2) When players have destroyed the Steel Watch Foundry.\r\n3) When players have killed Gortash."
